<div id="comment_status_64612233" class="commentstatus"></div>
<div id="comment_64612233" class="cw">
	<div id="comment_top_64612233" class="commentTop newcomment">
		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64612233" name="comment_link_64612233" href="//yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23381587&amp;cid=64612233" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64612233)" >Celebratory Gunfire</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64612233" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64612233); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Whateverthisis">Whateverthisis</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Whateverthisis">( 7004192 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64612233">		
		on Tuesday July 09, 2024 @09:34AM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23381587&amp;cid=64612233">#64612233</a>)
		<small> </small>
</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64612233">Most states have laws against <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Celebratory_gunfire" title="wikipedia.org">Celebratory Gunfire</a> [wikipedia.org] that ranges from a misdemeanor to a felony to fire a gun into the air.  You're running a serious risk by firing into the air, especially if you miss as the bullets may come down and hit someone.  It's not clear legally where the line is drawn yet in terms of destruction of property vs. invasion of privacy or trespassing on private property, but for damned sure if you miss and that bullet comes down on your neighbor or goes through a neighbor's window you should expect to be arrested.<p>

Stick to high pressure water hoses or baseball bats or some such.  Guns are very risky.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64612233">
<span class="ind"></span><a id="reply_link_64612233" class="btn link" href="//yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23381587&amp;op=Reply&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;pid=64612233" onclick="D2.replyTo(64612233); return false;">Reply to This</a> 	<a href="#" class="comment_share_toggle btn link">Share</a>
